data.description: ***This is it***3.75% FHA Assumable Loan***Over an Acre horse property fully fenced, No HOA, backyard with a pergola, pavers, swing set, Shed, 70 & 30 AMP ele. set up for out buildings/RV hook ups, additional watering system close to another out building. Plenty of room for a mare stall. Ground set 2020 manufactured home 2x6 with living room, family room, dining room with a breakfast bar, kitchen with farm sink in the island, range hood, plenty of cabinets and a pantry with a barn door, split bedrooms, the primary suite has a walk in closet, double sinks, private toilet room, soaking tub and separate shower, 2nd bathroom with double sinks and separate door to tub/ toilet room, additional bedrooms with walkin closets. Laundry room with cabinets, recessed lighting, ceiling fans throughout Best deal currently with the FHA qualifying assumable loan on the market on a acre plus in Wittmann.
